{"tid":583064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾50人堵九巴荔枝角車廠入口　阻巴士回廠","createTime":"2018-03-06T16:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T18:26:46.000Z","uid":5195,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b6446ae2df636cce74e62adc594d142a499a1a","tid":583064,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"【12:46】九巴九巴傳訊部副主管林子豪凌晨12時45分在荔枝角車廠門外會見記者，指九巴車務總監梁健宏及企業策劃及業務發展總經理蘇偉基準備約見4名被解僱車長，並且提醒他們九巴是有上訴機制，上訴委員會可對被解僱離職員工提出的上訴進行覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n【12:36】工會、月薪車長大聯盟成員及政黨人士逾50人於凌晨12時30分開始靜坐，以及堵塞荔枝角車廠入口，其他回廠九巴須在道路上「兜圈」，未能成功進入荔枝角車廠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/165729/thumbnail/645552d70094334f11a28a690d955306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F165729%2Fthumbnail%2F645552d70094334f11a28a690d955306.jpg&h=cc0428fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7488fb03f9b0b54b50bdf5921c8739a2e60e30e2","tid":583064,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4e84a989a79200a69b75652d50f2d69101a111","tid":583064,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ed83a3602f4adf76bd8fd5d1853a284142a2715","tid":583064,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9e6ac7eb69a1de92768fe07a518f91b0ba0e93","tid":583064,"uid":55924,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"聽朝搭狗巴果陣就指撚住個司機叫佢咪撚搞咁多野 努力番工 爭乜鳩取加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/d